data.description: Amazing newly rehabbed 2 unit building that's located on a quiet street near the Humboldt Park and the 606 trail. This ready to move in multi-unit features renovated kitchens with new cabinets and quartz counter tops. Includes renovated bathrooms with new lighting and fixtures. You will find beautiful hardwood floors throughout the units. Has updated plumbing, electrical and HVAC. This is a wonderful opportunity to live in a highly desirable area with being able to rent out one unit and live in another unit. Do not miss out on this amazing deal and schedule a showing today!
